revisions.description: Updated contact info.

Added the following traps: cienaCesDpTsMeterFloodContainerTotalThresholdExceeded cienaCesDpTsMeterFloodContainerTotalThresholdNormal Added the following objects: cienaCesDpTsMeterFloodContainerAttachmentTotalRateState
Added cienaCesDpPortShapingSubscriptionExceedsOperSpeed and cienaCesDpPortShapingSubscriptionWithinOperSpeed traps
Added Queue-Group-Instance identifer for Sub Port
Added l2pt mac translation attribute for Access Flow
Updated name of cir to controlPlaneUsedCir in Scheduler Instance
Converted cirWeight to cirPercent and added eirPercent
Added tap-point attribute to scheduler-instance. Added cir-policy, eir-policy, cirWeight to scheduler-profile Added cirWeight to queues of queue-group-profile Added cir to scheduler-instance
Added object - cienaCesDpSubPortEgressGeneratorMac for generator MAC address of the egress reflector
Adding variable for learn limit in virtual-switch Rlan table as cienaCesDpVirtualSwitchRlanLearnLimit.
Added root-scheduler shaper overspeed attribute
Adjusted range for cienaCesDpVirtualSwitchRlanIndex object to allow value 0.

Defined cienaCesDpTsMeterProfileColorMode at cienaCesDpTsMeterProfileEntry 7. Defined cienaCesDpTsQCAProfileWREDMaxQueueSize at cienaCesDpTsQCAProfileWREDEntry 4. Defined cienaCesDpTsQCAProfileWREDMinQueueGuarantee at cienaCesDpTsQCAProfileWREDEntry 5. Defined enumeration l2Rcos(26) under cienaCesDpTrafficClassTermPresentType.
Add new shaper-compensation for Queue-Group-Profile
Add new rcosPolicy for Dscp+Mpls-TC, add new l4-application traffic-class-term
Add missing liAttach Types

New L2-CFT Profile table added. Also reference to L2-CFT profile table entry from VS-table. Also new per-L2-CFT-Profile L2-CFT-Protocol table added which is analaguous to old per-VS L2-CFT Protocol table
Fixed MIB errors
New PFG Profile table added. Also reference to PFG profile table entry from VS-table.
New MEF Coupling Flag object added to cienaCesDpTsMeterProfile.

New objects are added to cienaCesDpTsMeterFloodContainerNotifAttrs. New tables are added for traffic services namely cienaCesDpTsMeterProfile,cienaCesDpTsCosMapRcos, cienaCesDpTsCosMapFcos, cienaCesDpTsShaperProfile, cienaCesDpTsQCongestionAvoidanceProfile,cienaCesDpTsQRCOSQMap, cienaCesDpTsQGroupProfile,cienaCesDpTsQGroupInstance, cienaCesDpTsQSchedulerProfile and cienaCesDpTsQSchedulerInstance under. cienaCesDpSubPort, cienaCesDpVirtualSwitch, cienaCesDpTrafficClassTerm,cienaCesDpQosFlow, cienaCesDpAccessFlow ,cienaCesDpPbtTransit and cienaCesDpCpuSubInterface are added as new nodes under cienaCesDpMIBObjects.
Initial creation.
